# [main.py](file:///home/adhiraj-singh/track_project/main.py) — Complete Architecture & Implementation Plan

> **YOLOv8 + DeepSORT Real-Time Object Tracker with PySide6 GUI**

---

## 1. High-Level System Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph Entry["🚀 Application Entry"]
        A["__main__ block"] -->|creates| B["QApplication"]
        B -->|instantiates| C["MainWindow"]
        C -->|calls| D["window.show()"]
        D -->|starts| E["sys.exit(app.exec())"]
    end

    subgraph Init["🏗️ MainWindow.__init__"]
        C -->|builds| F["PySide6 UI Components"]
        C -->|loads| G["YOLOv8n Model (CPU)"]
        C -->|initialises| H["DeepSORT Tracker"]
        C -->|creates| I["QTimer (30 ms interval)"]
    end

    subgraph UI["🖥️ GUI Layer (PySide6)"]
        F --> F1["QLabel — Video Display"]
        F --> F2["QPushButton — Upload Video"]
        F --> F3["QPushButton — Use Camera"]
        F --> F4["QPushButton — Start Tracking"]
        F --> F5["QPushButton — Stop Tracking"]
        F --> F6["QPushButton — Stop Video"]
    end

    subgraph Signals["🔗 Signal → Slot Connections"]
        F2 -->|clicked| S1["open_video()"]
        F3 -->|clicked| S2["use_camera()"]
        F4 -->|clicked| S3["start_tracking()"]
        F5 -->|clicked| S4["stop_tracking()"]
        F6 -->|clicked| S5["stop_video()"]
        I  -->|timeout| S6["update_frame()"]
    end

    subgraph Pipeline["⚙️ Frame Processing Pipeline"]
        S6 -->|reads frame| VP1["cv2.VideoCapture.read()"]
        VP1 -->|tracking ON?| VP2{"tracking_enabled?"}
        VP2 -->|Yes| VP3["process_frame()"]
        VP2 -->|No| VP4["Raw frame"]
        VP3 --> VP5["YOLOv8 Inference"]
        VP5 --> VP6["Extract Detections (xyxy → xywh)"]
        VP6 --> VP7["DeepSORT update_tracks()"]
        VP7 --> VP8["Draw Bounding Boxes + IDs"]
        VP8 --> VP4
        VP4 --> VP9["BGR → RGB Conversion"]
        VP9 --> VP10["QImage → QPixmap"]
        VP10 --> VP11["Display on QLabel"]
    end

    subgraph Loop["🔁 Video Loop Behaviour"]
        VP1 -->|ret=False| LP1["Reset to frame 0 (infinite loop)"]
        LP1 -->|next tick| VP1
    end

    style Entry fill:#1a1a2e,stroke:#e94560,color:#fff
    style Init fill:#16213e,stroke:#0f3460,color:#fff
    style UI fill:#0f3460,stroke:#533483,color:#fff
    style Signals fill:#533483,stroke:#e94560,color:#fff
    style Pipeline fill:#1a1a2e,stroke:#e94560,color:#fff
    style Loop fill:#16213e,stroke:#0f3460,color:#fff
```

