> [main.py](file:///home/adhiraj-singh/track_project/main.py) wraps it in a **PySide6 GUI**; [track.py](file:///home/adhiraj-singh/track_project/track.py) is a headless **CLI** version.  
> [app.py](file:///home/adhiraj-singh/track_project/app.py) is an unrelated Streamlit chatbot that uses Gemini AI.
